name: IFOOP (I Feel out of Place)
description:
You're immensely shy, any social interaction scares you like crazy. You feel out of place...

The first game I ever made, doing sprites took ages so the gameplay isn't really good.

(Everything was made by me)

I would have preferred to do an arcade game but the theme inspired me this.
